SieveOfEratosthenes = (n) ->
    prime = Array(n + 1).fill(true)

    i = 2
    while i*i <= n
        if prime[i] is true
            for j in [2 * i...n] by i
                prime[j] = false

        i += 1

    string = ""
    for i in [2...n]
        if prime[i] is true
            string += i + " "

    console.log string
